    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped sweet potato</strong> to one side of a baking tray, then drizzle with 1/2 tbsp [3/4 tbsp] [1 tbsp] <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Add the<strong> coated chicken</strong> to the other side of the tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until everything is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
