    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>bulgur</strong> <strong>wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for an initial 2 min</p>",
