    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roughly chop your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Once the bulgur has had 2 min, add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> and<strong> blanched edamame beans</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 5-7 min or until everything is cooked through and tender</p><p>Once tender, drain and return to the pot</p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong> to the tray with the chicken and sweet potato and cook for a further 2-3 min or until toasted and golden</p>",
