      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> baby leaf salad</strong> and<strong> roasted sweet potato</strong> to the drained bulgur and veg, then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>bulgur salad</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> finely on a clean board</p>",
